      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Detail of outcome</h2>

      <div class="consultation-outcome-detail">
        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Summary of responses we received, along with the government’s response outlining the next steps.</p>

<p>Read the updated <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/elective-home-education">elective home education</a> guidance documents for local authorities and parents.</p>
