      <section class="original-consultation">
        <header>
          <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="original-consultation-title">Original consultation</h2>

        </header>


    <section class="app-c-banner app-c-banner--grid" aria-label="Notice">
      <h2 class="app-c-banner__title">Summary</h2>
  <p class="app-c-banner__desc">
          Call for evidence on greater oversight of children whose parents elect to educate them at home, and consultation on revised DfE guidance documents.
        <br></br><br></br>
        <strong>This consultation was held on <a href="https://consult.education.gov.uk/school-frameworks/home-education-call-for-evidence-and-revised-dfe-a/">another website</a>.</strong>

  </p>

    <p class="app-c-banner__desc">        This consultation ran from<br></br><span class="consultation-date"><time datetime="2018-04-04T12:00:00.000+01:00">midday on 4 April 2018</time> to
        <time datetime="2018-07-03T00:00:00.000+01:00">11:59pm on 2 July 2018</time></span>
</p>
</section>


      </section>


    <div class="consultation-description">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Consultation description</h2>

      
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This consultation has 2 parts.</p>

<p>The first is a call for evidence on issues connected with elective home education. In particular:</p>

<ul>
  <li>registration of children educated at home</li>
  <li>monitoring of home education provision</li>
  <li>support for home educators</li>
</ul>

<p>The second part is seeking comments on draft versions of 2 <abbr title="Department for Education">DfE</abbr> guidance documents about elective home education. One is designed for local authorities and the other for parents.</p>

</div>
</div>


    </div>


